{"tid":2119323,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大灣區聘港澳居民　出國旅行要申請","createTime":"2020-07-22T04:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T08:38:16.000Z","uid":6497,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"30ad7d34bcc586d6eb82feac2c70a600e712515c","tid":2119323,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200722/RDRU2YRYZZ5AI37ESXVUZBCOSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FRDRU2YRYZZ5AI37ESXVUZBCOSQ%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=3b541d4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FRDRU2YRYZZ5AI37ESXVUZBCOSQ%2F&h=6fffe960\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200722/RDRU2YRYZZ5AI37ESXVUZBCOSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港社會兩極化，許多人有出走移民的念頭，相反亦有「漏夜趕科場」的人，願意到大灣區找尋發展機會。廣東省人力資源和社會保障廳本月公佈《粵港澳大灣區（內地）事業單位公開招聘港澳居民管理辦法（試行）》的通知》（簡稱：《通知》），內容要求到事業單位的應徵者，要擁護中國共產黨領導和社會主義制度，維護祖國的統一、安全、榮譽和利益等。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。根據網上資料，雖然不同地區有不同要求，凡因私事出國者，基本都需要向上級申報有關地點和原因，獲批後始可出行。"},{"pid":"1d2dcf780bf5da50f084b8f487729a57a3b633a2","tid":2119323,"uid":152476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"好多機遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb652f35d3e29241d88a6dc56f3a8c0b13a3fb3d","tid":2119323,"uid":190333,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"啱哂對上鏗鏘集果個ocean"},{"pid":"429aa3675284c80a0cc5765a4b7dadee8d4df47d","tid":2119323,"uid":152476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:48:45.000Z","msg":"《通知》指，管理辦法對象為無外國居留權的港澳居民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=