oji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8006582ef2cced972008fccb2f4b6e928d2d5173","tid":2119323,"uid":173002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"係英國搬磚嘅人工都高過嗮去強國啦。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90372c007abb2ecfae98bcac1b532286520ec52","tid":2119323,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"見工都要宣誓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c0b7da2e0abed0d3cba1c963515f20354b7f7f","tid":2119323,"uid":216828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582852300f0396ecffe237e736b27b104dfbd0a3","tid":2119323,"uid":260570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"腥港人拿拿臨死返上去先啦"},{"pid":"99aec98c8248861b33107fa509450a567d888290","tid":2119323,"uid":352001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:35:18.000Z","msg":"沒收香港人外國護照，睇下會唔會第三次世界大戰"},{"pid":"aa3fe791857139604c1f46a2ac96d247bb7f3411","tid":2119323,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"共享中國人的榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家咁好！前途咁好！點解要出國？"},{"pid":"55f4dad32693ee668f59b74731859ccdbc5aeda7","tid":2119323,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"070ad9afb0876cd20046f1f1a94b2f05f30a975e","tid":2119323,"uid":292788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"大家笑鳩大灣區，好快香港會請大灣區人。"},{"pid":"538abe13b6b4ef079a